<h3>Adult Media Swapper's Privacy Policy</h3>
 
<p>
AMS is dedicated to giving you a private and secure browsing experience. AMS collects general information only 
for the purpose of statistical analysis. For example: we may tally the total number of queries for a particular category and share this information with our 
advertisers and sponsors. We will NOT however, create a personal profile about your particular searches and share this information.
</p>

<p>
AMS does not share your account information or e-mail address with anyone. From time to time, we do send e-mail 
updates to members who have opted to receive these when they set up their account. If you do not wish to be contacted, do not select these options when 
you create your account. You can update your preferences at any time by going to the <a href="../../account/">Account Info</a> section and logging in.
</p>

